OL,3,CLiz Truss says she had to urge British
OL,4,Cdiplomats to be more pro-Israel at UN
OL,6,FFormer prime minister has told ITV
OL,7,FNews she had to "intervene" to get
OL,8,FBritish diplomats to adopt a more pro-
OL,9,FIsrael stance at the UN.
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV News Political Editor
OL,12,FRobert Peston she said had advocated a
OL,13,Fmore pro-Israel policy while foreign
OL,14,Fsecretary and prime minister.
OL,16,FShe said: "While I was Foreign
OL,17,FSecretary, on some occasions, I had to
OL,18,Factively intervene with officials to
OL,19,Fget them to vote in a more pro-Israel
OL,20,Fway, at the United Nations.
