OL,3,CLiz Truss says she had to urge British
OL,4,Cdiplomats to be more pro-Israel at UN
OL,6,F"So there definitely is a tendency to
OL,7,Fnot support Israel as much as I would
OL,8,Flike in the Foreign Office. And I
OL,9,Fthink that always needs to be
OL,10,Fchallenged."
OL,12,FMs Truss has been speaking to the
OL,13,Fmedia ahead of the publication of her
OL,14,Fbook: Ten Years to Save the West where
OL,15,Fshe outlines her time in government as
OL,16,Fwell as her wider political view on
OL,17,Fthe future issues the UK and other
OL,18,Fcountries face.
