OL,3,CLiz Truss says she had to urge British
OL,4,Cdiplomats to be more pro-Israel at UN
OL,6,FShe recently made headlines by
OL,7,Fendorsing Donald Trump to win the US
OL,8,F2024 General Election saying the world
OL,9,Fwas a safer place during Mr Trump's
OL,10,Fprevious term.
OL,12,FWhile doing her media tour Ms Truss
OL,13,Fwent as far as telling the BBC she did
OL,14,Fnot "see a purpose for the UN as it
OL,15,Fstands."
OL,17,FShe said: "At present, it has been
OL,18,Fvery ineffective at dealing with
OL,19,Finternational situations, in fact
OL,20,Fpositively damaging, for example, on
OL,21,FIsrael."
