OL,3,CLiz Truss says she had to urge British
OL,4,Cdiplomats to be more pro-Israel at UN
OL,6,FWhile speaking to ITV's Peston the
OL,7,Fformer PM also said she did not
OL,8,Fbelieve the Bank of England governor
OL,9,FAndrew Bailey should not stay in his
OL,10,Fjob for his handling of the Autumn
OL,11,F2022 crisis.
OL,13,FShe went on to say: "So everybody
OL,14,Fmakes mistakes. And I think senior
OL,15,Fholders of public office senior
OL,16,Fofficials have to be allowed to make
OL,17,Fmistakes. Otherwise, they really
OL,18,Fwouldn't be in a job for very long."
