OL,3,CLiz Truss says she had to urge British
OL,4,Cdiplomats to be more pro-Israel at UN
OL,6,FBut added: "What they (the BoE)
OL,7,Factually did is make it pretty clear
OL,8,Fthrough various public statements,
OL,9,Fbriefings, that they did not support
OL,10,Fthe government's fiscal policy. And I
OL,11,Fthink that's a problem for democracy."
OL,13,FMs Truss's tenure in Downing Street
OL,14,Flasted just 49 days after her mini-
OL,15,Fbudget triggered mass market turmoil.
