OL,3,CLiz Truss says she had to urge British
OL,4,Cdiplomats to be more pro-Israel at UN
OL,6,FThroughout the course of the
OL,7,Finterview, the ex-PM outlined how she
OL,8,Fbelieved she was not given enough
OL,9,Fwarning of the crisis in the pension
OL,10,Ffunds that troubled the UK's bond
OL,11,Fmarket so much.
OL,13,FShe conceded that if she was aware of
OL,14,Fthe "tinderbox" she would not have
OL,15,Fgone ahead with the mini-budget that
OL,16,Fsparked panic in the markets.
OL,18,FBut she also said she was under the
OL,19,Fimpression at the time that there was
OL,20,Fno sense the mini-budget "would be
OL,21,Fmassively provocative to the markets."
