OL,3,CLiz Truss says she had to urge British
OL,4,Cdiplomats to be more pro-Israel at UN
OL,6,FMs Truss went on to say there should
OL,7,Fbe an investigation into the BoE's
OL,8,Fhandling of the autumn 2022 crisis
OL,9,F"because what it felt like to me, and
OL,10,Fcertainly looking at in retrospect, is
OL,11,Fthey tried to shift the blame for the
OL,12,Fmarket reaction entirely onto the
OL,13,Fgovernment, whereas they've been
OL,14,Fresponsible for the critical policy
OL,15,Flever of monetary policy."
